--- !u!114 &5407164532943900388
MonoBehaviour:
  m_ObjectHideFlags: 0
  m_CorrespondingSourceObject: {fileID: 0}
  m_PrefabInstance: {fileID: 0}
  m_PrefabAsset: {fileID: 0}
  m_GameObject: {fileID: 6062183090467887795}
  m_Enabled: 1
  m_EditorHideFlags: 0
  m_Script: {fileID: 11500000, guid: 0f939d5fcafb87a49902064df3aa78d0, type: 3}
  m_Name: 
  m_EditorClassIdentifier: 
  attacks:
  - attack: {fileID: 6039413959020384239}
    randomChance: 6
  - attack: {fileID: 2867648504411925385}
    randomChance: 7
  - attack: {fileID: 4131379115905150938}
    randomChance: 4
  attackCooldown: 10
  spriteRenderer: {fileID: 7001180856553086688}
  miniBoss: 0
  SecondPhase: 0
  _player: {fileID: 0}
  attackCooldownTimer: 5
  grounded: 0
  bounceOffWall: 0
  faceTowardPlayer: 0
  hardMode: 1
  Dialogue:
  - "Well now, look who\u2019s wandered into me clover patch. A tall, quiet human
    with that \u201CI want gold\u201D look in their eyes. Typical."
  - "Not a word out of you, eh? Fine. I\u2019ll do the talking. Someone has to."
  - "Let me guess \u2014 you\u2019re here for me pot o\u2019 gold. Everyone always
    is. Never \u201CHow are you, Leprechaun?\u201D or \u201CWould you like a snack?\u201D
    No. Straight to the treasure."
  - "Still staring. Wonderful. You\u2019ve the social energy of a mossy rock."
  - "If you\u2019re thinking of grabbing me gold, I should warn you \u2014 I bite.
    And I run fast. Faster than you, I\u2019d wager."
  - "Oh, don\u2019t give me that look. I\u2019ve seen it before. \u201COoooh, shiny
    coins!\u201D Yes, yes, very impressive. They\u2019re mine. All mine. Generations
    of hoarding. You can\u2019t have even one."
  - "\u2026You\u2019re still not talking. Are you enchanted? Cursed? Or just rude?"
  - "Fine. Take a shamrock. Not the gold \u2014 just the shamrock. And be off with
    you before I start throwing tiny shoes."
  - "And don\u2019t come back unless you bring snacks. Preferably something with
    sugar."
  RepeatDialogue:
  - Back again to challenge the lucky St. Patrick once more? you already lost (attempt_count)
    times
  - 'I see your back again, do you want a reminder to never fight the lucky St. Patrick.I
    will make your attempts:  (attempt_count) turn to infinity.'
  - I'm getting board killing you can we just end this fast, like all other fights.
    You have already lost around (attempt_count) times. Lets just end this fast.
  dialogueTypingSpeed: 0.02
  DialogueImage: {fileID: 0}
  dialogueTxt: {fileID: 0}
  trueDialogueTypingSpeed: 0
  DontDoDialouge: 1
